Titolo: Moe Chronicle

Anno: 2014

Descrizione: Moe Chronicle, commonly known in Japan as Genkai Tokki Moero Chronicle (限界凸記 モエロクロニクル, Genkai Tokki Moero Kuronikuru), is a dungeon crawler role-playing video game developed by Compile Heart for the PlayStation Vita. It is the second game in Compile Heart's Genkai Tokki series of video games, following Monster Monpiece and preceding direct sequel Moero Crystal and Genkai Tokki: Seven Pirates. Moe Chronicle was released on May 15, and an Asian release featuring Chinese and English subtitles was later published by Sony Computer Entertainment and released on May 5, 2015. It was then released on Steam with English, Japanese and Chinese subtitles on August 16, 2017 as Moero Chronicle. On April 26, 2019 the game was released as Moero Chronicle Hyper on the Nintendo Switch with preorders opening for a physical version later that year.

